[SHORT DESC]
User is made invulnerable for one turn, then hits the next turn. 30% chance to paralyze.

[LONG DESC]
<p>User is made invulnerable for one turn, then hits the next turn. Has a 30% chance to paralyze the target. Sky Uppercut and Thunder have regular accuracy and base power against a Pokémon in the middle of Bounce. The base power of Gust and Twister doubles against a Pokémon in the charge up stage of Bounce.</p>
<h2>Related Moves</h2>
<p><a href="/rs/moves/fly">Fly</a> is almost identical, but with less power and more accuracy.</p>